         <div subtype="original" type="letter" xml:id="L.1933" xml:lang="en">
            <pb facs="#IMG.1" n="1"/>
            <dateline>Colombo, 16 August 1891</dateline>
            <opener>Dear Sir,</opener>
            <p>Many thanks for the treatise on <ref target="https://gams.uni-graz.at/o:hsa.languages#L.183">Malayan Portuguese</ref>, which I have looked through with interest. I hope you will be able to bring out a work on <ref target="https://gams.uni-graz.at/o:hsa.languages#L.180">Ceylon Portuguese</ref>. I shall be glad to help you as far as I can. There have been no recent works published.</p>
            <closer>
               <salute>Yours truly</salute>
               <lb/>
               <signed>
                  <persName ref="[authorityLink]">Donald Ferguson</persName>
               </signed>
            </closer>
            <pb facs="#IMG.2" n="2"/>
         </div>
